Original Articles
The effect of phasic auditory alerting on visual perception
Anders Petersen a,⇑, Annemarie Hilkj ær Petersen b, Claus Bundesen a, Signe Vangkilde a, Thomas Habekost a
a Department of Psychology, University of Copenhagen, Denmark
